title.narrative: USAID Competitiveness, Trade and Jobs (CTJ) in Central Asia

description.narrative: The Competitiveness, Trade, and Jobs activity in Central Asia will increase the competitiveness of Central Asian economies by working with firms in industries that have high growth potential for exports and have the potential to create a large number of jobs. The activity will also work with governments to address policy and regulatory constraints to moving goods across borders more efficiently.
